Hugging Face Endpoints allows access to straightforward model inference.
Coupled with Pinecone we can generate and index high-quality vector embeddings with ease.
Let's get started by initializing an Endpoint for generating vector embeddings.

We click on Create new endpoint, choose a model repository (eg name of the model), endpoint name (this can be anything), and select a cloud environment.
Before moving on it is very important that we set the Task to Sentence Embeddings (found within the Advanced configuration settings).
